Usage: exportNdr [-help] <ndrRuleName> {-def <file_name> | -lef <file_name>}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<ndrRuleName>             # name of NDR rule (string, required)
-def <file_name>          # DEF file name (string, required)
-lef <file_name>          # LEF file name (string, required)